    "extract": "Adelaide Productions, Inc. (also referred to as Columbia TriStar Television Animation) is a copyright holding company division of Sony Pictures Television that was founded on April 12, 1993, by Columbia Pictures Television. It's responsible for the animated series for the studio.\nAfter a period of dormancy, Adelaide Productions became a television production division for Sony Pictures Animation in 2018. Adelaide Productions remains an active subsidiary of Sony Pictures Television, holding the copyrights to its previous productions."
